{"tid":1999283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lisa遭死亡威脅「我要殺她槍準備好了！」　恐怖網友P墳墓圖惡毒詛咒","createTime":"2020-05-03T05:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T06:35:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9886cb31a0cc05e98e225867b60f21ea7bd20a0e","tid":1999283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK的泰籍成員Lisa人美實力強，近期在大陸選秀節目《青春有你2》擔任舞蹈導師，知名度更上一層樓，不過近日卻傳出遭到死亡威脅，引起粉絲高度關注。<br />\n<br />\nInstagram上有個帳號，取名方式是以辱罵IU和Lisa，該網友近日在限時動態放話：「Lol I will kill lisa. I have my gun already.（我會殺了Lisa，槍已經準備好。）」仇恨式的內容引起粉絲議論，害怕他真的對Lisa做出傷害舉動。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此該網友還將Lisa的照片和墳墓P在一起，譏笑「死了多好」，另一名網友則是在推特發文，撂下狠話如果Blackpink回歸，就會射殺Lisa，要粉絲現在可以先和偶像說掰掰了。<br />\n<br />\n對此，粉絲緊急在各大社群平台上發文，包括推特、IG、微博，號召所有粉絲標註泰國大使館及YG公司，希望讓官方注意網友的激進言論，保護好Lisa避免恐怖事件真的發生，同時也譴責暴力，呼籲網友冷靜點。"},{"pid":"96312efb637b122eb6ea491161360c1dcd548010","tid":1999283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4854/4854146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4854%2F4854146.jpg&h=af19d030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Lisa遭死亡威脅。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4854/4854147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4854%2F4854147.jpg&h=63b3d0ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d484ab08b2fe5e7b67a7ca0ded8cc1eb109758fd","tid":1999283,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"如果要殺我瑛瑛 真係唔知典算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae97ff30f945c4d1f0e97ded654c31da6977b83","tid":1999283,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"一睇就知樓主做的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=